  "body": "#### What type of PR is this?\r\n\r\n/kind bug\r\n\r\n#### What this PR does / why we need it:\r\n\r\nManual pick of https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/pull/114319\r\n\r\nUpdates golang.org/x/net to pick up the fix for CVE-2022-41717.\r\n\r\nThis is needed in addition to updating the go version to pick up the bundled version of this dependency.\r\n\r\n```release-note\r\nUpdates golang.org/x/net to fix CVE-2022-41717\r\n```",
